Configuring the limiter
=======================

useHighOrderLimiter should always be true.

Standard 4thO PPM
-----------------
CRDparam::g_usePPMlimiter = true
CRDparam::g_useFlattening = true
CRDparam::g_useHighOrderLimiter = true
g_limitFaceValues = true

* You can turn off both limiting and flattening

4th order central
-----------------
CRDparam::g_usePPMlimiter = true
CRDparam::g_useFlattening = false
CRDparam::g_useHighOrderLimiter = true
g_limitFaceValues = false

1st order Godunov scheme
------------------------
CRDparam::g_usePPMlimiter = false
CRDparam::g_useFlattening = true or false
CRDparam::g_useHighOrderLimiter = true
g_limitFaceValues = true or false

